    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Hunt Logic AI ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our hunting technology platform.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3>Account Information</h3>
    <ul style="padding-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Name, email address, phone number</li>
      <li>Payment information (processed securely via Stripe)</li>
      <li>Account preferences and settings</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Hunting Data</h3>
    <ul style="padding-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Trail camera photos and analysis results</li>
      <li>GPS waypoints and hunting locations</li>
      <li>Hunting journal entries and success records</li>
      <li>Weather preferences and alert settings</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Usage Data</h3>
    <ul style="padding-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>App usage patterns and feature interactions</li>
      <li>Device information and operating system</li>
      <li>Analytics and performance data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Provide AI-powered hunting predictions and recommendations</li>
      <li>Analyze trail camera photos for species recognition</li>
      <li>Improve our machine learning models and predictions</li>
      <li>Send hunting alerts and notifications</li>
      <li>Process payments and manage subscriptions</li>
      <li>Provide customer support</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Protection & Security</h2>
    <p>Your hunting locations, trail camera photos, and personal data are encrypted both in transit and at rest. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information.</p>

    <p><strong>Your hunting spots are private.</strong> We never share your GPS waypoints or specific hunting locations with other users or third parties.</p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do NOT sell your personal information. We may share data only in these circumstances:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Aggregated, anonymized data for improving AI models (no personal identifiers)</li>
      <li>With service providers (payment processing, cloud hosting) under strict confidentiality agreements</li>
      <li>When required by law or to protect our legal rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Request data correction or deletion</li>
      <li>Opt out of AI model training using your data</li>
      <li>Export your hunting data</li>
      <li>Cancel your account at any time</li>
    </ul>

